### Indian Sub Division Rainfall Data from 1901 - 2015

Rainfall data for Indian sub-division area from 1901-2015 and from January - December. 


### Some Tasks
- All the sub-division with driest and wettest year & month
- Wettest Sub-Division 
- Driest Sub-Division
- Heavy rainfall (probable flooding?)
